{"pin":"BH00006","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00006","anchor":"","title":"Lawh-i-Sarraj","first_line":"Thy letter hath been made present before the Throne and hath reached the Seat of Him Who is known through naught else but Himself, and that which it contained [3.5s]... ...Shake off, O heedless ones, the slumber of negligence, that ye may behold the radiance which His glory hath spread through the world.","first_line_orig":"نامه آنجناب بین یدی العرش حاضر و بر مقر انه لایعرف بما سواه واصل و ما فیه  ","language":"5","word_count":"26800","subjects":"@infallibility; sinlessness ['ismat], @walking the spiritual path; spiritual wayfaring; the virtuous life, @spiritual transformation, @collection; ordering of the Sacred Writings, @power and sovereignty of God; omnipotence of God, @station of the Manifestation of God, @proofs of the Manifestations of God, @the power of words; of speech, @Manifestation of God speaking in the voice of Divinity, @power of the Manifestation of God","notes":" \u003ca href=\"https://d9263461.github.io/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V2/Contents.html\"\u003eROB2.262 et al\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://bahai-library.com/bahailib/1504.pdf#page=152\"\u003eMMAH.140\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#242\"\u003eLL#242\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","ty